description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '10 Minute Guided Breathwork For Stress & Anxiety I Feel Calm and Focused' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Discover the power of full, deep breathing with our 10 minute guided breathwork session, specially created to reduce stress and enhance focus. This technique, dirga pranayama, not only teaches you how to take full breaths for relaxation and mental clarity but also aids in improving lung capacity, making it beneficial for asthmatics and anyone looking to optimize their breathing technique. Ideal for beginners and experienced practitioners, this calming exercise is your gateway to mindfulness and a healthier, more focused mind.
